Title: End of Line
Plot: When Daniel finally sets a deadline for resetting the U-87 Cylon - and unknowingly ending Zoe-A?s existence as she knows it - she makes a desperate attempt to save herself. But when her plan backfires, she finds herself out of time and out of options.
GuestStars: Alex Arsenault, James Marsters, Genevieve Buechner, Hiro Kanagawa, Juan Riedinger
